# Conformance harness: the TS dumps under tests/conformance/out-ts{,-sem}/ are
# committed as the GOLDEN baseline — CI regenerates them and asserts `git diff`
# is clean, so any change to TS dump output surfaces in review (catches TS-side
# drift the cross-language diff alone would miss). Kotlin dumps stay generated
# (under build/, ignored above) and are diffed against this baseline.

